                <h2 class="section-heading">What is weather and its types?</h2>
                <p>It is what the sky and the air outside are like. Such as cold or cloudy. There are six types of weather: <br>
                    i. Sunny: Sunny days are usually pleasant as most people like doing activities outdoor.</p>
